snippet.title: Top 10 Most Expensive Dog Breeds in the World

localized.description:
Top 10 most expensive dogs in the world. These are some of the best dog breeds for guard dogs. They are also very dangerous and expensive dog breeds. This list include the following dogs:
1 German Shepherd 
2 Cavalier King Charles Spaniel 
3 Samoyed
4 English Bulldog 
5 Chow Chow 
6 Rottweiler 
7 Tibetan Mastiff 
8 Pharaoh Hound 
9 Bearded Collie 
10 Akita 

Which is the fastest dog in the world?
